data.description: Welcome to this stunning end-of-group colonial townhome located in the desirable Prospect Green community. This meticulously maintained property features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, providing a perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entering the main level foyer, you are greeted by a tastefully carpeted family room, offering a cozy space for relaxation, along with convenient storage options. The upper level boasts an open floor plan adorned with gleaming hardwood floors and recessed lighting. The inviting living room showcases a gas fireplace, setting the ambiance for warmth and comfort. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient island with a breakfast bar. Adjacent to the kitchen is a spacious dining area, ideal for entertaining. Completing this level is a convenient half bath. Ascend to the second upper level, where hardwood flooring seamlessly flows throughout. The primary suite is a retreat with a tray ceiling, an attached bath offering dual vanity sinks, a soaking tub, a stall shower, and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share an attached bath, providing both comfort and functionality. A dedicated laundry area adds convenience to your daily routine. Step outside to enjoy the outdoors on the deck or patio, surrounded by a fully fenced rear yard, ensuring privacy and a perfect space for outdoor activities. The property also includes a 2-car attached garage for your parking convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Prospect Green townhome your new home, where modern amenities and thoughtful design come together to create an exceptional living experience. Schedule your showing today!
